result.title: WRONG ANSWER ON CODEFORCES , SHOWING DIFFERENT OUTPUT
result.content:
Hello everyone , i am new to codeforces and as i was solving my first problem "SPREADSHEETS" from codeforces beta round #1 , which is showing wrong_answer in test1 , while in my g++ compiler its giving correct output for that case ...please anyone help....why is this happening??

THIS IS LINK TO MY CODE::::

http://ideone.com/25zz0L

TEST CASE : 2 R23C55 BC23

ANSWER : BC23 R23C55

ON MY COMPUTER : BC23 R23C55

CODEFORCES SHOWING : BC23 R23C54

Why is codeforces showing 54 instead of 55?
